feedback_history.text:
-= Kitchen =-
Look at you, bigshot, walking into a kitchen like it isn't some huge deal.

You can see a fridge. The fridge contains a white onion and a cilantro. A fridge... Is that really what you were looking for? You see an oven. You can see a table. You shudder, but continue examining the table. You see a knife on the table. If you haven't noticed it already, there seems to be something there by the wall, it's a counter. On the counter you can make out a cookbook. If you haven't noticed it already, there seems to be something there by the wall, it's a stove. But oh no! there's nothing on this piece of junk.

There is an open sliding patio door leading south. There is an open plain door leading west. There is an exit to the north. Don't worry, there is no door.
